Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.39,0:00:11.83,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.83,0:00:12.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:14.10,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.11,sign_305_4_Field_Trip_Notic,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Field Trip Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:18.53,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,A lunchbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:22.11,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Field trip, next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.11,0:00:23.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:25.00,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Make one!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:27.56,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. What kind of lunch would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:30.84,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry, Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:32.66,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:34.83,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm better at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:41.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:44.17,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! I'm better than the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:47.39,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm even better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.39,0:00:50.35,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Look at you talk, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:00:59.06,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like we'll have to settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:04.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the master \Nof the house, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:08.42,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:11.20,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Field trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.73,0:01:13.21,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,lunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.75,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,competition! Three round match!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.97,sign_1930_24_Field_Trip_Lunch,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Field Trip Lunch Competition\NThree Round Match!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:53.65,sign_4132_27_The_Next_Day,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(112,1)}- The Next Day -
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:55.65,sign_4188_28_Commentator_____,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Commentator               Judge              Head Judge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.28,sign_4212_29_Commentator_____,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Commentator   Judge   Head Judge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You guys even prepared this set?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:06.32,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,You'll each be making three dishes:\Na salad, a meat course, and a dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:10.63,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Use all your skills and entertain me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:13.20,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What is your character even \Nsupposed to be anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.50,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,The ingredients are your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.09,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Stay within budget as you \Nmake your decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.49,0:03:21.29,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Be sure not to strain \NMiss Kobayashi's wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:23.67,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.67,0:03:24.67,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.26,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.85,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,They're both driven to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.66,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi's into it.
