Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.37,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.57,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,First dish, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:59.00,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Contestant Kobayashi's appears \Nto just be cherry tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.59,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Did you throw the match?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:04.71,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mine's a seafood and paprika Caesar salad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.28,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's no comparing the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.48,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's no need to compare them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.97,Main,Fafnir,0000,0000,0000,,The winner of the first round is Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.60,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:22.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How did my special salad lose \Nto these cherry tomatoes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.73,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.33,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:33.12,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you didn't \Nunderstand what a lunchbox is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:34.50,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,Contestant Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:36.72,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,The amount you prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.57,0:04:39.09,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.84,sign_6806_68_Shock_,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win next round!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.06,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.06,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.06,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.06,0:04:56.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Bacon and eggs don't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.81,sign_7117_77_Head_Judge,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Head Judge
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.81,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Hamburger's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But bacon and eggs are delicious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.85,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Hamburger's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.84,sign_7218_77_Head_Judge,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Head Judge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.56,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,They're no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:08.27,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I often asked my parents \Nto make them though...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.28,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Last is the dessert round.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.65,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Something in a cup, or a fruit, would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.28,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You're to bring one item that isn't cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:19.75,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.48,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,This is unusual, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:25.89,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,For you and Miss Kobayashi to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.91,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:37.84,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.48,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,This is deplorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:42.45,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,What's so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.60,0:05:47.35,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to see Tohru like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.57,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What should I bring for the third dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.58,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.23,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:56.82,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Because!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:13.40,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,This fight only happened because \Nyou've grown so close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.59,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:17.27,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should call it pro-wrestling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.68,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Every now and then is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She may be a maid,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.81,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,but she can be my friend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:34.69,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you and a \Ndragon are equals, human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.93,0:06:37.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,At least, Tohru and I both feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.92,sign_9639_110_Mini_Jellies,Bag,0000,0000,0000,,Mini {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H02A6B1&}Jellies
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.92,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we fought today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is Tohru still gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.02,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Close enough to fight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.01,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:57.97,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.87,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.18,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Miss Kobayashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:08.64,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.09,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.77,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:16.79,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm not going to lose either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:19.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I need to take off my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.50,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,Third round complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.34,sign_10658_130_Orange,,0000,0000,0000,,Orange
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.18,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, would you like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:32.85,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.93,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.80,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Where do they sell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.39,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The shopping district, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:44.58,Main,L,0000,0000,0000,,She's done it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:45.31,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's my first time seeing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:53.52,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've won this round!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:56.19,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.71,Main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Items from the other world \Nare against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:14.65,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.92,0:08:23.15,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:24.05,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.54,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Even after everything, \Nyour food's still delicious, Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you flatterer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.44,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's dessert, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:37.50,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tohru?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:58.17,Main-Top,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought I'd \Nfind you hiding out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.74,Main-Top,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.43,sign_12920_149_Elma,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(355,1)}Elma
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.73,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Our room...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.77,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten the laws?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.10,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Dragons disrupt the order of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:08.69,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,You're returning with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:13.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, I see you're as damn stiff, \Nstrict, and persistent as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:19.84,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tohru and Lady Elma \Nare on very bad terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.68,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.34,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Like cats and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.34,0:09:25.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you learn that idiom at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.00,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:33.33,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they're about to explode \Nany second, but will things be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.97,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Last time they fought
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.42,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,three islands disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:39.34,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:43.34,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Our power's equal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.34,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,but this time I'll settle the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:52.81,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she can calmly let her \Nstomach growl in this tense situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.14,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Dragons are imp—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:57.64,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe not. She looks embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.65,Blush,,0000,0000,0000,,Blush
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:01.01,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,You've being very distracting, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:05.65,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite the attitude from \Nsomeone who just destroyed my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:10.04,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Please follow our laws before you \Ntry protecting order in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:14.51,Main-Top,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:13.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Even Tohru wouldn't do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:14.95,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.18,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:20.53,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why am I the one apologizing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.90,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She's easily influenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:26.17,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she doesn't seem like a bad person,\N so why don't you get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:28.44,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We're from different factions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:31.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Not all dragons are united in thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.89,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's the harmony faction \Nthat values law and order,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:37.00,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,the chaos faction that yearns \Nfor chaos and destruction,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:40.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,and the spectating faction that doesn't \Nwork with either group or each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:41.46,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:45.95,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So Elma belongs to the harmony faction, \Nand I'm with the chaos faction,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:47.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,so we oppose each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.84,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So you're one of the villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.34,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:55.75,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a good dragon, \Non my best behavior in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That sounded forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:10:58.42,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.57,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you home, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:02.29,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,By force, if I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:03.96,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:07.18,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eliminate you from \Nthis world without a trace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:08.43,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Take this somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.33,0:11:14.61,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I've prepared another dimension, \Nso we'll do this there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.02,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.02,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:22.65,Italics,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised to see the fiendish \NTohru listening to a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.03,Italics,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.15,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:29.49,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You cheated!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:33.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I simply respected order like she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:36.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It was a peaceful resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.94,0:11:40.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, time to fix what she destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:43.41,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where'd you send her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.88,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The field Kanna and I played in before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.15,0:11:50.25,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:52.48,sign_17041_212_The_Next_Day,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,- The Next Day -
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:54.74,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you trick me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.85,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you sent \Nme to another continent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:00.56,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:05.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy as long as I can quietly \Nbe a maid in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:07.04,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:08.74,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.41,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:12.88,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,You're planning to take over \Nthis world, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:13.94,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:14.68,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:15.74,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I will take you—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:18.63,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.09,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you eaten anything since yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:28.59,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not from this world, \Nso I can't interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.35,sign_17949_228_Cream_Bread,Bag,0000,0000,0000,,Cream Bread
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, something like this should be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.97,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Here, want some? It's cream bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:43.05,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I'll kindly take you up on the \Noffer to help restore my strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.77,Italics,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.98,Italics,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? This is super good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:54.74,Italics,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,It's melting in my mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.87,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm energized now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:00.09,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Time for our rematch, Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.00,Main-Top,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave, I'll give you all of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.01,sign_18738_229_Cream_Bread,Bag,0000,0000,0000,,Cream Bread
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.48,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.44,Italics,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Huge balls are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.94,Italics,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,balls are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:33.70,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.04,sign_19510_243_Episode_8,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 8
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.04,sign_19510_244_New_Dragon__Elma,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,New Dragon, Elma! (She's Finally Appearing, Huh?)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:42.41,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:43.78,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.60,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be working with you starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:48.48,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Joui Elma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.68,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.13,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.75,0:13:55.64,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on? Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:58.41,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask you the same, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:14:03.90,sign_20036_252_Emergency_Exit,Door,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Exit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.68,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This is where I work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:01.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:03.90,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So this is just a coincidence? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:06.13,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.82,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm investigating the cultural \Nstandards to see if beings from
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.78,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,the other world really can integrate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:12.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:14.91,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,She did say you were with \Nthe harmony faction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:18.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, can you do this job?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.91,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use magic, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:22.08,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Silly question!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.50,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can't do human labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:26.94,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.51,Italics,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.05,Italics,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.60,Italics,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,What is this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.55,Italics,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,What is everyone doing with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.63,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Something popped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:40.20,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:41.69,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.30,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then push this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:49.43,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Human, you do some pretty difficult work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:53.66,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,But I've memorized romanized\Ncharacter input or whatever, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:55.24,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,so I won't stay behind anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.20,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:15:00.20,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, when will I earn \Nmy pay for today's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:03.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, a month from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:06.41,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I can't receive it tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:10.65,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,No. We total out at the end of \Nthe month, and today's the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:11.38,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.14,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do for rent and food?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you commute from the other world...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:21.25,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, could it be that you can't go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.06,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.85,0:15:27.97,Main-Top,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't possess enough power to \Nopen the gate between worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:31.57,sign_22211_289_She_came_through,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,She came through the gate Tohru opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:31.02,Main-Top,K,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your power was equal to Tohru's?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.64,Main-Top,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just as strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.11,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,But we were born different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:37.78,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.79,sign_22451_295_Takiguchi_Butche,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Takiguchi Butchery
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:41.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:44.70,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure you've got a lot \Non your plate, but hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:49.10,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to be working with me, \NI'll have you learn a lot more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:50.83,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,You have my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:55.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Those are hot, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:55.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.91,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:11.10,Italics,K,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I should keep quiet \Nabout meeting Elma today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:12.98,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.98,0:16:14.48,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.65,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,For tonight's dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.26,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:22.60,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,There's a strange smell on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:23.59,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.74,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you secretly cheating on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not! Today at work...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:31.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,An office romance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:33.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You've picked up another weird phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.60,Italics,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.80,Italics,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,Can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.05,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.53,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your work today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:16:59.44,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:02.78,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You've learned a lot about \NPC operation, huh, Elma?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.33,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:06.45,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prove myself useful at this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:08.75,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you've still got a ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.95,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Kobayashi, sweet chestnuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:12.53,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some sweet \Nchestnuts on the way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:14.22,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,They're delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.63,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.01,sign_4132_27_The_Next_Day,,0000,0000,0000,,- Sunday -
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.52,0:17:22.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since my last day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.81,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take it easy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:26.10,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:31.97,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean everything so you can enjoy your \Nday off in a clean room, Miss Kobayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.07,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.90,sign_25273_335_Kobayashi_Kanna,Plug,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi Kanna
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful for that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:44.78,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.78,0:17:50.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,When I get serious,\N I can make a room spotless of all dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:54.90,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's brand new, as if Shiva passed through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.11,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Even the furniture's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:59.13,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,A space for relaxation \Ndoesn't need any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:04.12,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy sleeping to your heart's \Ncontent in this spacious room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.21,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,As if I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:07.62,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Put it all back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.45,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:10.56,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.73,Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.31,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:16.72,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.11,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:20.24,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make breakfast,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.38,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,be it a full course meal \Nor an imperial feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shall I slaughter a cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.81,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a light breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.81,0:18:29.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.04,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.16,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.25,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.68,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,They look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.02,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What meat's in—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:40.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:44.51,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to satisfy your lust,\N not just your appetite?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:45.76,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:46.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.69,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:48.97,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tail, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:55.57,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.69,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.15,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're oddly gung-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.37,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.01,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:07.65,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're spinning your wheels though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.83,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you've reverted to how you\N were when you first came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.45,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:18.29,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine. I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:19.79,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:22.56,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:23.55,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Elma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:26.65,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:28.78,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,You're always helping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:30.51,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,So I brought something to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:31.88,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:32.93,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,A protective charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.16,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,It turned out well, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:38.00,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's handmade? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:40.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.48,0:19:41.94,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.44,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.44,Main,Elma,0000,0000,0000,,Today I'm taking you ba—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.87,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone, Elma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.06,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kobayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.67,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.80,Main,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I'm holding back \Nand putting up with it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.54,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you're being mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:21.86,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I work hard too,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.20,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,wanting lots and lots of praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:28.26,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting you to pet my head a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:35.65,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not used to being wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:43.40,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's never happened to me before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.37,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a clue what to do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:52.22,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Often I think human relationships \Nare just confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.97,0:20:55.67,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I even put distance \Nbetween myself and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:21:00.60,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I've had friends, but never close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:04.20,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,So here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:09.08,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:13.04,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make it any clearer than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:15.48,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Take the hint, take the hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.28,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:27.46,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:29.55,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you a protective charm, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.17,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You'll gain the protection of evil gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:32.40,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:33.99,Main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:51.74,Main,Lucoa,0000,0000,0000,,You're surprisingly forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.74,0:21:54.46,Main,Shouta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:28.01,sign_33687_420_Next_Episode,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,189)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.70,0:23:29.41,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru! You're too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:30.84,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,You know that yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:31.92,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Elma, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.92,0:23:32.91,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.91,0:23:35.67,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,For now, please put down the \Ncream bread you're holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:37.72,Main,E,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're good, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:40.01,sign_33951_426_Episode_9,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Episode 9
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:40.01,sign_33951_427_Sports_Festival_,Screen,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Sports Festival! (There's No Twist Or Anything)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:38.85,Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
